I '''Ernst Karl Abbe''' (Eneru, 1840 &ndash; Eenru 14, 1905) metung yang  [[Germany|Aleman]] [[physicist]], [[optometrist]], [[entrepreneur]], ampong mapanibayu keng pangaguman. Kambe da ri [[Otto Schott]] ampong [[Carl Zeiss]], iya ing mitatag keng makabayung [[optics (salamin mata)]]. I Abbe menalkus yang dakla gamit keng salamin mata. Kayabe ya kareng mikibandi keng [[Carl Zeiss AG]], metung a Aleman a talagawa kareng optical systems.

Ing bakung [[Abbe (crater)|Abbe]] keng [[bulan]] mipalagiu ya kaya bilang karangalan.

